# LiVEiT® Colour Palette

Colour is a fundamental part of the LiVEiT® visual identity.

The official palette has been designed to provide clear visual recognition while supporting accessibility, consistency and intuitive navigation throughout the LiVEiT® Framework.

Each colour has a defined purpose and should be used consistently across applications, documentation and supporting material.

---

# Core Brand Colour

The primary LiVEiT® brand colour is Aqua.

| Colour | Hex       |
| ------ | --------- |
| Aqua   | `#7EBECD` |

This colour represents the LiVEiT® Framework and should be used for primary branding, highlights and official visual identity wherever appropriate.

